<h1>
UPDATE: 2021 Changes to Your Anti-Money Laundering Obligations </h1>
<div class="post-details">
<span class="date">
May 12, 2021 </span>
<br />
<br />
<span class="section">CATEGORY:</span>
<a href='/about-bcrea/practice-tips' class='postCategory'>Practice Tips</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
<br />
<span class="section">TAGS:</span>
<strong>
<a href='/tag-search?tag=2021-fintrac-changes' class='postCategory'>2021 FINTRAC Changes</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
<a href='/tag-search?tag=anti-money-laundering' class='postCategory'>Anti-Money Laundering</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
<a href='/tag-search?tag=fintrac' class='postCategory'>FINTRAC</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
<a href='/tag-search?tag=land-owner-transparency-act' class='postCategory'>Land Owner Transparency Act</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
<a href='/tag-search?tag=land-owner-transparency-registry' class='postCategory'>Land Owner Transparency Registry</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
</strong>
</div>
<div class="author">
<span class="photo" style="background-image: url(https://www.bcrea.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/marianne.jpg);"></span>
<span class="details">
Posted by<br>
Marianne Brimmell<br />
Communications Specialist </span>
</div>
